    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> cfallin created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13689#discussion_r3438332963\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The blockorder algorithm implementation is the wrong place to hide this logic, IMHO -- it's otherwise a low-level and generic algorithm. Maybe an <code>f.is_effectively_cold(block)</code> helper that encodes this logic would be better?</p>\n</blockquote>",
